R Graph Gallery;
RAND Visualizations Page;
Pew Research Center Favorite Data Visualizations of 2025;
ESPN Analytics;
Spurious Correlations;
Python Graph Gallery;
Silver Bulletin;
The Pudding.

Pick one plot you find. In your .qmd, write:

A link or description of the plot.
Which of the five genres it belongs to (or whether it’s a hybrid).
What question it answers in one sentence.
One thing it does well. (Clear labels? Good color choice? Reveals a pattern?)
One thing you’d change. (Misleading axis? Too many categories? Cluttered?)



